  m_Name: CareyFosterBridge
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LabData
  heading: Carey Foster's Bridge to Measure Specific Resistance of Material
  details: "Carey Foster\u2019s Bridge is an electrical circuit used to measure the
    specific resistance of a material with high accuracy.\nIt compares the unknown
    resistance of a wire sample with known resistances using a nearly balanced bridge
    condition.\nThis method allows precise determination of resistivity by minimizing
    measurement errors and using a sliding contact."
